We explored the migration patterns of two-neutrophil squads at asymmetric bifurcations (Fig. 7a). The cross-sections of the branches are 3 × 5 µm2 and 10 × 5 µm2 and their length is equal. The hydraulic resistance R of the channels is different, estimated using the following equation101\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
